metadata.name: Gaze MMXXIII
metadata.description:
With 'Gaze MMXXIII' I want to offer a special artwork to all. 

This piece showcases the being who has inhabited my imagination and creative expression for over a decade. 

Expanding from my 2020 release, 'Gaze', this new iteration offers the audience a look at the growth my work and aesthetic have taken both creatively and technically. 

Thank you for sharing this journey of growth and expression with me so far.
